===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}
# {{lb|en|historical}} The summer capital of [[w:Kublai Khan|Kublai Khan]]'s empire.
#* {{RQ:Coleridge Christabel|page=55|passage=In '''Xanadu''' did {{smallcaps|Kubla Khan}} / A stately pleasure-dome decree: / Where {{smallcaps|Alph}}, the sacred river, ran / Through caverns measureless to man / Down to a sunless sea.}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{lb|en|figurative}} A place full of beauty, happiness and wonder.
